TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Relatively monster free zone, for now...

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Two coms are shipwrecked on a monster infested isle with no prospect of rescue. Your objective is to destroy the two monster factories in the north. Watch out for amphibious monsters ;)

TriggerLogic.Text: The monsters will take about 7 minutes to notice you.
